com.alexkasko.rest.handlers
Class HandlersDispatcher

java.lang.Object
  com.alexkasko.rest.handlers.HandlersDispatcher

public class HandlersDispatcher
extends Object

Dispatches request using handlers registry matching with regular expression. Contains separate registries for GET, POST and PUT requests. Registries are ordered in handlers registration order. First matched handler will be used. Dispatcher must be created by application and placed into ServletContext using dispatcherKeyInServletContext parameter of HandlersDispatcherServlet Handler patterns are registered using named-regexes.

Author:
alexey Date: 4/4/12
